de.upb.t2t.model

Class Variety

  • java.lang.Object
    • de.upb.t2t.model.Variety
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Abbreviable, java.lang.Comparable<Variety>

    public class Variety
extends java.lang.Object
implements Abbreviable, java.lang.Comparable<Variety>
    A rather static class that contains a list of all varieties that have been parsed from the database on startup. A Variety consists of an ID, its proper name and said names abbreviation.
    Author:
    Michel May (michel-may@gmx.de)
